---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Advanced Medical Textiles | OEKO-TEX Certified 4-Way Stretch Fabric" 
  description="Explore the science behind Yilong Scrubs. From moisture-wicking technology to anti-microbial finishing, we innovate medical apparel fibers."
  keywords="Polyester Rayon Spandex, 4-way stretch fabric, OEKO-TEX medical fabric, antimicrobial scrubs, moisture-wicking medical uniforms"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-center italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Advanced Medical Textile Collection</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg italic text-slate-600">We don't just manufacture apparel; we innovate the very fibers medical professionals wear. Our fabric systems are the result of 20 years of continuous refinement.</p>
    
    <div class="rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl mb-32 h-[500px]">
      <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A11493834b4ac48288484ad3adb699ac8V.png" alt="Wholesale Medical Scrub Fabric Rolls" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-32">
      <div class="p-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic text-primary">Elite Comfort Blend</h3>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-6 italic">72% Poly / 21% Rayon / 7% Spandex</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 italic text-sm text-slate-500">Rayon provides an ultra-soft, silky touch, while Polyester ensures durability and Spandex delivers superior elasticity.</p>
        <div class="text-primary font-bold italic text-xl underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">205 GSM</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic text-secondary">Pro-Active Performance</h3>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-6 italic">Polyester / Spandex Core</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 italic text-sm text-slate-500">Advanced moisture-wicking capillary action to keep you dry through the longest shifts.</p>
        <div class="text-secondary font-bold italic text-xl underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">180 GSM</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-sm text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic text-blue-500">Air-Flow Tech</h3>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-6 italic">Lightweight Poly-Mesh Tech</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 italic text-sm text-slate-500">Optimized for maximum breathability. Perfect for hot-climate medical environments.</p>
        <div class="text-blue-500 font-bold italic text-xl underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">130 GSM</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Vibrant Color Palette</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-8 italic text-slate-600">Color is identity. We offer a sophisticated range of medical colors that are reactive-dyed for maximum color fastness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A06c4adcbc1864fe3a78b56ab652195d3N.png" alt="Available Medical Scrub Colors Palette" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>